Text: RE Dave Dronets BirthdayExcellent Original Message From SMTP Sent Thursday October PM To Subject RE Dave Dronets Birthday Were in Original Message From Dronet Elizabeth ENRON Sent Thursday October PM To Tonks Colin Pimenov Vladi Ames Chuck Pehlivanova Biliana Berryman Kyle Reed Stuart Marolo Massimo Piazze Tara Chiu Lindon Schlesinger Lauren Subject Dave Dronets Birthday Hi everyone Daves birthday is on Saturday November rd and we would love for you to join us We are planning to eat at Buca di Beppo on the Buffalo Speedway I have reserved the Popes Table for pm If you would like to come please RSVP Feel free to invite whoever you want to come along Here is a map to the restaurant mapmodegeolatlon id fid Hope to see you there Elizabeth Dronet This email is the property of Enron Corp andor its relevant affiliate and may contain confidential and privileged material for the sole use of the intended recipient s Any review use distribution or disclosure by others is strictly prohibited If you are not the intended recipient or authorized to receive for the recipient please contact the sender or reply to Enron Corp at and delete all copies of the message This email and any attachments hereto are not intended to be an offer or an acceptance and do not create or evidence a binding and enforceable contract between Enron Corp or any of its affiliates and the intended recipient or any other party and may not be relied on by anyone as the basis of a contract by estoppel or otherwise Thank you
